works.description: To honor the 50th anniversary of Russian cosmonaut Yuri Gagarin’s first manned space flight, Montegrappa, one of the Italy’s most reputed manufacturers of fine writing instruments, has unveiled a new set of limited edition pens. The barrels of the commemorative pens come engraved with the image of Yuri Gagarin in bas-relief, which is further bordered with an interplanetary motif. The caps of the pens feature the coat of arms of the USSR. The pocket clip is edged by reproductions of Moscow’s monument to Yuri Gagarin, which was completed in 1980.
